net.customware.gwt.dispatch.client.DispatchAsync
public class CachingDispatchAsync
extends net.customware.gwt.dispatch.client.standard.StandardDispatchAsync

Dispatcher which support caching of data in memory. It also avoids simultaneous executions of the same action, which is very useful in development.
